{"tid":1532532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手聽討呢條藍絲𡃁模","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:36:51.000Z","uid":118716,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9ee2a6095d2e1520d3f7dbb2e52338bf8c84f7c2","tid":1532532,"uid":118716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0ttUuo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0ttUuo.png&h=88a4c3fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wrvonK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wrvonK.png&h=4382511e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點係最後一句！最後一句！我地忘記左林鄭，連口號都廢事嗌呀！</span></strong></span>我地搞地鐵，搞警察，唔係唔搞得，但係我地而家運動係失焦呀！我地要憾動既係政權、係制度，試想下，如果由民主制度選出一個政府，其餘四大訴求有咩難度？所以，我地要帶返個運動去正軌！「五大訴求」太局限、「光復香港時代革命」太空泛。應該要將呢場運動升級去民主運動，「林鄭下台」、「真民主」應該要成為主軸！<br />\n可能你會覺得林鄭係廢，但佢在制度上係領導角色，幾廢都好，唔可以唔當佢係首要目標，我敢講，而家警隊最驚係林鄭下台，警隊洗濕個頭，一定要同林鄭共存亡，所以唔該，「林鄭下台」呢個主題一定要拎番出黎！"},{"pid":"868ff1d6312da8d5b88a9a4d6c679d20e24eef79","tid":1532532,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"呢d 垃圾咪po 上黎洗版la"},{"pid":"98f328110a81e3040f2c5b8119fefd8bd0d34199","tid":1532532,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"j 圖"},{"pid":"f27f2bcf4183bed3b425b5cd4294323d57831354","tid":1532532,"uid":118716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"睇字得唔得呀屌你"},{"pid":"161bd4a1fa2d198b5a9d5f2ba8a23dc39ffc0e40","tid":1532532,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"明明係差佬想殺人，倒轉晒嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0147e2c077572920cd02eae996b860278b32692","tid":1532532,"uid":197149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:25:13.000Z",